### [1 Chronicles Chapter 18](../../../bib/kjv/ch1018.htm#001.md)

[1 Chronicles](../../../bib/kjv/ch1001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">ch1 18:0</span></span>

Overview

[Ch1 18:1](../../../bib/kjv/ch1018.htm#001.md), David subdues the
Philistines and the Moabites; [Ch1
18:3](../../../bib/kjv/ch1018.htm#003.md), He smites Hadarezer and the
Syrians; [Ch1 18:9](../../../bib/kjv/ch1018.htm#009.md), Tou sends Hadoram
with presents to bless David; [Ch1
18:11](../../../bib/kjv/ch1018.htm#011.md), The presents and the spoil
David dedicates to God; [Ch1 18:13](../../../bib/kjv/ch1018.htm#013.md), He
puts garrisons in Edom; [Ch1 18:14](../../../bib/kjv/ch1018.htm#014.md),
David's officers.

